---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/hub.css';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="The Web Foundry — Modern Websites for Cincinnati Small Businesses"
  description="The Web Foundry designs and builds modern, custom websites for Cincinnati small businesses. Latest technology, zero templates, real results."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- ── Navigation ── -->
  <nav class="nav" id="nav">
    <div class="container nav__inner">
      <!-- Logo B: unified wordmark + locale — swap to logo-a markup for thewebfoundry.org -->
      <a href="#" class="nav__logo logo-b">
        <span class="logo-b__name">The Web Foundry</span>
        <span class="logo-b__locale">Cincinnati</span>
      </a>
      <ul class="nav__links">
        <li><a href="#mission" class="nav__link">Mission</a></li>
        <li><a href="#showcase" class="nav__link">Work</a></li>
        <li><button class="nav__cta js-open-modal">Get in Touch</button></li>
        <li><a href="/about" class="nav__link">About</a></li>
      </ul>
      <button class="nav__hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Menu">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main id="main-content">
  <!-- ── Hero ── -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hero__bg-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero__noise" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero__glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container hero__inner">
      <div class="hero__eyebrow reveal">
        <span class="hero__eyebrow-dot"></span>
        Built in Cincinnati
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero__headline">
        <span class="hero__word" style="animation-delay:0.15s">Your</span>
        <span class="hero__word" style="animation-delay:0.30s">next</span>
        <span class="hero__word" style="animation-delay:0.45s">website?</span>
        <br/>
        <span class="hero__word hero__word--accent" style="animation-delay:0.65s">It's</span>
        <span class="hero__word hero__word--accent" style="animation-delay:0.80s">on us.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero__sub reveal reveal-delay-3">
        We design, build, and launch modern websites for Cincinnati small businesses — completely free. You focus on running your business. We'll handle the rest.
      </p>

      <div class="hero__actions reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <a href="#showcase" class="btn btn--primary">See the Work</a>
        <button class="btn btn--ghost js-open-modal">Let's Talk</button>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__scroll-hint reveal reveal-delay-6" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hero__scroll-line"></div>
        <span>Scroll</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- ── Mission ── -->
  <section class="mission" id="mission">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-tag">Our Mission</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">The web shouldn't be<br/><em>a luxury</em></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mission__content">
        <div class="mission__beat reveal">
          <p>Your business is the one people count on. You've built something real — a reputation, a following, a place in this community. But your website? It doesn't tell that story.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission__rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="mission__beat reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <p>Getting a real website built has always been <em>expensive and confusing.</em> Agencies quote thousands. DIY tools leave you with something generic — and something you have to maintain, test, and troubleshoot yourself.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission__rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="mission__beat reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <p><em>AI changed the game.</em> We build in days what used to take weeks. And we think that speed should benefit the businesses that need it most — not just the ones with the biggest budgets.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission__rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="mission__beat reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <p>So we design, build, and launch your website — <em>for free.</em> Custom design, modern tech, built to represent what you actually do. After launch, everything is handled — hosting, security, updates — for less than what you're paying today.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Showcase ── -->
  <section class="showcase" id="showcase">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-tag">Featured Work</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">See what's possible<br/><em>for your town</em></h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Three businesses. Three completely different aesthetics. All built with AI — all built with intention.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="projects-grid">

        <a href="/showcase/bakery" class="project-card" id="card-bakery" data-theme="bakery">
          <div class="project-card__visual">
            <div class="project-card__mock project-card__mock--bakery">
              <div class="mock-nav"></div>
              <div class="mock-hero">
                <div class="mock-headline"></div>
                <div class="mock-sub"></div>
                <div class="mock-btn"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-cards">
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card__overlay">
              <span class="project-card__view">View Site →</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-card__info">
            <div class="project-card__tag">Bakery & Café</div>
            <h3 class="project-card__name">Sweet Crumb Bakery</h3>
            <p class="project-card__desc">Warm, artisan aesthetic with floating pastry animations and an online menu experience.</p>
            <div class="project-card__palette">
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#FDF6EC"></span>
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#C9926B"></span>
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#7A9E82"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/showcase/plumber" class="project-card" id="card-plumber" data-theme="plumber">
          <div class="project-card__visual">
            <div class="project-card__mock project-card__mock--plumber">
              <div class="mock-nav"></div>
              <div class="mock-hero">
                <div class="mock-headline"></div>
                <div class="mock-sub"></div>
                <div class="mock-btn"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-cards">
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card__overlay">
              <span class="project-card__view">View Site →</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-card__info">
            <div class="project-card__tag">Home Services</div>
            <h3 class="project-card__name">Peak Flow Plumbing</h3>
            <p class="project-card__desc">Bold, conversion-focused industrial design with animated trust signals and emergency CTA.</p>
            <div class="project-card__palette">
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#1A2744"></span>
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#FF6B2B"></span>
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#F5F5F5"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/showcase/salon" class="project-card" id="card-salon" data-theme="salon">
          <div class="project-card__visual">
            <div class="project-card__mock project-card__mock--salon">
              <div class="mock-nav"></div>
              <div class="mock-hero">
                <div class="mock-headline"></div>
                <div class="mock-sub"></div>
                <div class="mock-btn"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-cards">
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
                <div class="mock-card"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card__overlay">
              <span class="project-card__view">View Site →</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-card__info">
            <div class="project-card__tag">Beauty & Wellness</div>
            <h3 class="project-card__name">Lumière Salon & Spa</h3>
            <p class="project-card__desc">Luxe editorial aesthetic with champagne tones, masonry gallery, and elegant booking flow.</p>
            <div class="project-card__palette">
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#1C1410"></span>
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#E8D5C4"></span>
              <span class="swatch" style="background:#C9A96E"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── How It Works ── -->
  <section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <span class="section-tag">How It Works</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Three steps.<br/><em>That's it.</em></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline__line" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="timeline__step reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="timeline__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">We talk</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">We learn about your business, your style, your goals. No jargon, no pressure — just a conversation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__step reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="timeline__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">We build</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">AI-powered design and development. We iterate fast until it feels right — and looks even better.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline__step reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="timeline__marker" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="timeline__content">
            <h3 class="timeline__title">You launch</h3>
            <p class="timeline__desc">Your new site goes live. We handle everything after — hosting, security, updates. You never have to think about it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CTA ── -->
  <section class="cta-section" id="contact">
    <div class="cta-section__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container cta-section__inner">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="section-tag section-tag--light">Let's Talk</span>
        <h2 class="cta-section__title">Ready for a website<br/>that works as hard as you do?</h2>
        <p class="cta-section__sub">Reach out — we'd love to learn about your business and show you what's possible.</p>
        <button class="btn btn--cta js-open-modal">
          Let's get started
          <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  </main>

  <!-- ── Footer ── -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer__inner">
      <!-- Logo A: split style — matches thewebfoundry.org brand direction -->
      <div class="footer__logo logo-a">
        <span class="logo-a__primary">The Web</span>
        <span class="logo-a__secondary">Foundry</span>
      </div>
      <p class="footer__tagline">AI Vibe Coding for the people.</p>
      <nav class="footer__links" aria-label="Footer">
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer__copy">© 2026 The Web Foundry — Cincinnati. Built with ❤️ and AI.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    import '../scripts/main.js';
  </script>

  <!-- ── Contact Modal ── -->
  <div class="modal-overlay" id="contact-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="modal-title" hidden>
    <div class="modal-card">
      <button class="modal-close" id="modal-close" aria-label="Close">✕</button>

      <div class="modal-body" id="modal-body">
        <span class="section-tag">Let's Talk</span>
        <h2 class="modal-title" id="modal-title">Tell us about<br/><em>your business</em></h2>

        <form id="contact-form" novalidate>
          <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" style="display:none">

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="f-name">Your Name *</label>
              <input type="text" id="f-name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" placeholder="Maria Chen">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="f-email">Email Address *</label>
              <input type="email" id="f-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" placeholder="maria@example.com">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="f-phone">Phone (optional)</label>
            <input type="tel" id="f-phone" name="phone" autocomplete="tel" placeholder="(513) 555-0100">
          </div>

          <fieldset class="form-fieldset">
            <legend>Who is this for?</legend>
            <div class="form-radios">
              <label class="radio-label">
                <input type="radio" name="who_for" value="My business" checked>
                <span>My business</span>
              </label>
              <label class="radio-label">
                <input type="radio" name="who_for" value="Someone else's business">
                <span>Someone else's business</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="f-business">Business Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="f-business" name="business_name" required placeholder="Sweet Crumb Bakery">
          </div>

          <fieldset class="form-fieldset">
            <legend>Do you have an existing website?</legend>
            <div class="form-radios">
              <label class="radio-label">
                <input type="radio" name="has_website" value="yes" id="has-website-yes">
                <span>Yes</span>
              </label>
              <label class="radio-label">
                <input type="radio" name="has_website" value="no" id="has-website-no" checked>
                <span>No</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </fieldset>

          <div class="form-group" id="url-field" hidden>
            <label for="f-url">Website URL</label>
            <input type="text" id="f-url" name="website_url" placeholder="yourbusiness.com" pattern="[^\s]+\.[a-zA-Z]{2,}" title="Please include a domain extension (e.g. yourbusiness.com)">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="f-message">Anything else you'd like us to know?</label>
            <textarea id="f-message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about your business, goals, timeline..."></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="form-error" id="form-error" hidden></div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary form-submit" id="form-submit-btn">
            Send Message <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-success" id="modal-success" hidden>
        <div class="modal-success__icon">✓</div>
        <h3 class="modal-success__title">Message received!</h3>
        <p class="modal-success__sub">We'll be in touch within 24 hours. Check your email for a confirmation.</p>
        <button class="btn btn--ghost" id="modal-success-close">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
